<A NAME = "AE4920"></A><A HREF = "SPP19.HTM#AO54764"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Sensitive information to remain secure but enables law enforcement and national security authorities to obtain access to escrow-encrypted data in specific instances when authorized by law <P>
<A HREF = "SPP19.HTM#AO547129"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Escrowed encryption enables businesses and individuals to recover encrypted stored data to which access being lost and businesses to exercise greater degree of control over encrypted communications <P>
<A HREF = "SPP19.HTM#AO547232"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Escrowed encryption to dampen market for unescrowed encryption products to provide similar security without features for government exceptional access <P>
