<A HREF = "SPP19.HTM#AO549100"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Escrowed encryption schemes proposed to date intended to provide strong cryptographic confidentiality for users against unauthorized third parties <P>
<A HREF = "SPP19.HTM#AO549162"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>No confidentiality against authorized third parties having exceptional access <P>
<A HREF = "SPP19.HTM#AO55117"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Escrowed encryption provides lower degree of confidentiality <P>
<A HREF = "SPP19.HTM#AO551164"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Maintaining system security being difficult enough without deliberate introduction of potential security hole and introduction of another route of attack on procedures complicates job of information defender <P>
<A HREF = "SPP19.HTM#AO551243"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Adoption of escrowed encryption to lay into place mechanisms, procedures and organizations to be used to promulgate or enforce more restrictive cryptography policies <P>
