 Board, National<A NAME = "BB53257"></A><A HREF = "SPP25.HTM#BB680149"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A> Research Council, 2101 Constitution<A NAME = "AB53266"></A> Avenue, N.W<A NAME = "AB53271"></A>., Washington, D.C.  Telephone 202-334-2605 or e-mail CSTB<A NAME = "AB53293"></A>@
NAS.EDU.<BR>

[9] Note that the committee was quite aware of potential financial conflicts of interest among several of its members.  In 
accordance with established National Research Council procedures, these potential<A NAME = "AO53362"></A><A NAME = "AS53363"></A> financial<A NAME = "AB53366"></A> conflicts of interest were thoroughly 
discussed by the committee; no<A NAME = "AO53388"></A><A NAME = "AS53389"></A> one with a direct and substantial financial<A NAME = "AB533104"></A> stake in the outcome of the report served on the committee.

