<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO255104"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Requirement to encrypt wireless communications to accelerate shift to wireless modes of digital transport <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO2571"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Security in telephone switches to be improved in ways <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO257145"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Telecommunications service providers to provide services for link encryption of traffic on wired landlines <P>
<A NAME = "AE2630"></A><A NAME = "AE2630"></A><A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO2593"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>By addressing through telecommunications service providers public demands for greater security in voice communications known to be nonsecure <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO25969"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Government to maintain law enforcement access for lawfully authorized wiretaps through requirements imposed on carriers to cooperate with law enforcement in matters <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO259134"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Cellular telephone connects to PSTN through ground station <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO259165"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Cellular telephone service provider to feed traffic to PSTN in unencrypted form <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO259199"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Encrypted cellular telephone traffic from mobile handset to be decrypted at ground station <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO259253"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Legitimate law enforcement access not to be impeded by link encryption of cellular traffic until communications systems that bypass PSTN become common <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO26121"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Link security provided by service provider offers more opportunities for providing law enforcement with legally authorized access <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO26188"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>In case of voice communications, improved security over telecommunications network used for voice communications and provided by owners and operators of network <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO261201"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Devices used to provide end-to-end encryption of voice communications <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO261243"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Criminal user to go to trouble to obtain device to thwart lawfully authorized wiretap <P>
