<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO26328"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Voice being likely to be common form of communication used by general public <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO26378"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Committee recognizes that data communications to pose certain problems for law enforcement and focus of Recommendation 5.3 <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO26526"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>U. S. government to explore escrowed encryption for own uses <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO2679"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>U. S. government aggressively promoted escrowed encryption as pillar of technical foundation for national cryptography policy <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO26753"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Escrowed encryption having benefits and risks from public policy standpoint <P>
<A HREF = "SPP8.HTM#AO26792"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Committee believes that policy benefits to be gained by operational exploration of escrowed encryption by U. S. government <P>
<A NAME = "AE2800"></A><A HREF = "SPP9.HTM#AO2695"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Operational complexities of large-scale infrastructure being significant and prudent approach to policy to develop base of experience to guide policy decisions <P>
<A NAME = "AE2810"></A><A HREF = "SPP9.HTM#AO27166"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Information to conceal to be motivated to exploit technical circumventions of escrowed encryption <P>
<A NAME = "AE2820"></A><A NAME = "AE2820"></A><A HREF = "SPP9.HTM#AO2733"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Imposing particular solution to encryption dilemma being likely to have significant negative impact on natural market development of applications made possible by new information services and technologies <P>
<A NAME = "AE2830"></A><A HREF = "SPP9.HTM#AO27585"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Administration advocates of escrowed encryption being correct <P>
<A HREF = "SPP9.HTM#AO275106"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Private sector needs exceptional access to encrypted data for sound business reasons <P>
<A HREF = "SPP9.HTM#AO275140"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Law enforcement need for access to encrypted records to be substantially met by exercise of government's compulsory process authority for information relevant to investigation and prosecution of criminal activity against encrypted records and relevant cryptographic keys <P>
<A HREF = "SPP9.HTM#AO27711"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Committee believes that policy of deliberate exploration of concept of escrowed encryption being better suited to circumstances <P>
<A HREF = "SPP9.HTM#AO277168"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Way that encrypted communications come to pose significant problem for law enforcement <P>
