<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP10.HTM#AS3164">Recommendation 6: </A><DD>Committee makes Recommendation 6 based on observation 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP3.HTM#AS1172">Recommendations 4: </A><DD>Instances in which legislation to be needed found in Recommendations 4, 5.3 and 5.4 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP4.HTM#AS12393">Recommendations 4: </A><DD>Committee describes set of appropriate government interventions in Recommendations 4, 5 and 6 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP7.HTM#AS225201">Recommendations 5.3: </A><DD>Specific steps to be taken to mitigate difficulties as outlined in Recommendations 5.3 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP26.HTM#AS715317">Regulating Televised Presentations of Violence: </A><DD>Co-author of NRC publication Constitutional Issues in Regulating Televised Presentations of Violence in 1982 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP2.HTM#AS81121">Remediate certain important vulnerabilities: </A><DD>Doing impedes ability of nation to use cryptographic tools to help to remediate certain important vulnerabilities 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP10.HTM#AS3228">Representation of nongovernment interests: </A><DD>Policy-making process include better representation of nongovernment interests 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP1.HTM#AS3358">Research and development information: </A><DD>Businesses send through electronic channels amounts of confidential information bidding information, corporate strategies for expansion in critical markets, research and development information relevant to cost reduction or new products, product specifications and expected delivery dates 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP15.HTM#AS450117">Resolvable: </A><DD>Disputes in principle resolvable by U. S. Congress 
