by striking  sections 459, 461, and 462 of the Social Security Act (42 U.S.C. 659, 661, and 662)' and inserting  section 459 of 
the Social Security Act (42 U.S.C. 659)'.</ul></ul>
<p><ul>  (c) MILITARY RETIRED AND RETAINER PAY--</ul>
<p><ul><ul>  (1) DEFINITION OF COURT-- Section 1408(a)(1) of title 10, United States Code, is amended--</ul></ul>
<p><ul><ul><ul>  (A) by striking  and' at the end of subparagraph (B);</ul></ul></ul>
<p><ul><ul><ul>  (B) by striking the period at the end of subparagraph (C) and inserting  ; and'; and</ul></ul></ul>
