<A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO26128"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Section amended by striking on use of Federal courts <P>
<A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO261914"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Amendments made by subsection to be effective with respect to fiscal year 1997 and succeeding fiscal years <P>
<A NAME = "AK2621"></A><h3><center>Subtitle F---Establishment and Modification of Support Orders</center></h4><P><A NAME = "AK2624"></A><h3>SEC. 351. SIMPLIFIED PROCESS FOR REVIEW AND ADJUSTMENT OF CHILD SUPPORT ORDERS.</h3><P><A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO262951"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Upon request of parent or request of State agency under State plan or parent <P>
<A NAME = "AE12830"></A><A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO263011"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Review and adjust order in accordance with guidelines established pursuant to section if amount of child support award under order differs from amount to be awarded in accordance with guidelines <P>
<A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO263211"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Use automated methods to identify orders eligible for review <P>
<A NAME = "AE12850"></A><A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO2633105"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Making request for review and adjustment of order in accordance with child support guidelines established pursuant to section <P>
<A NAME = "AE12860"></A><A NAME = "AE12860"></A><A NAME = "AE12860"></A><A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO263410"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>NO PROOF of CHANGE in CIRCUMSTANCES NECESSARY in 3-YEAR CYCLE REVIEW, Procedures which provide that adjustment under clause to be made without requirement for proof or showing of change in circumstances <P>
<A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO2635114"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>State to review and adjust order in accordance with guidelines established pursuant to section <P>
<A NAME = "AE12880"></A><A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO26369"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>NOTICE of RIGHT to REVIEW, Procedures which require State to provide notice not less than once every 3 years to parents subject to order informing parents of right to request State to review and adjust order pursuant to paragraph <P>
<A NAME = "AK2638"></A><h3>SEC. 352. FURNISHING CONSUMER REPORTS FOR
CERTAIN PURPOSES RELATING TO CHILD SUPPORT.</h3><P><A NAME = "AE12900"></A><A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO26403"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Section 604 of Fair Credit Reporting Act amended by adding at end following new paragraphs <P>
<A NAME = "AE12910"></A><A NAME = "AE12910"></A><A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO264210"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Consumer report needed for purpose of establishing individual's capacity to make child support payments or determining appropriate level of such payments <P>
<A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO264311"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Paternity of consumer for child to which obligation relates established or acknowledged by consumer in accordance with State laws under which obligation arises <P>
<A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO264410"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Person provided at least 10 days' prior notice to consumer of which report requested that report to be requested <P>
<A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO264510"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Consumer report to be kept confidential <P>
<A NAME = "AK2648"></A><h3>SEC. 353. NONLIABILITY FOR FINANCIAL INSTITUTIONS PROVIDING FINANCIAL RECORDS TO STATE CHILD SUPPORT ENFORCEMENT AGENCIES IN 
CHILD SUPPORT CASES.</h3><P><A NAME = "AE12960"></A><A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO26503"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Part D of title IV amended by adding at end following <P>
<A NAME = "AK2652"></A><h3> SEC. 469A. NONLIABILITY FOR FINANCIAL INSTITUTIONS PROVIDING FINANCIAL RECORDS TO STATE CHILD SUPPORT ENFORCEMENT AGENCIES IN 
CHILD SUPPORT CASES.</h3><P><A NAME = "AE12980"></A><A NAME = "AE12980"></A><A NAME = "AE12980"></A><A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO265442"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Liable under Federal or State law to person for disclosing financial record of individual to State child support enforcement agency attempting to establish, modify or enforce child support obligation of such individual <P>
<A NAME = "AE12990"></A><A NAME = "AE12990"></A><A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO26557"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>PROHIBITION of DISCLOSURE of FINANCIAL RECORD OBTAINED by STATE CHILD SUPPORT ENFORCEMENT AGENCY <P>
<A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO265541"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>State child support enforcement agency which obtains financial record of individual from financial institution pursuant to subsection to disclose such financial record only for purpose <P>
<A NAME = "AE13010"></A><A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO265766"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Such individual to bring civil action for damages against such person in district court of United States <P>
<A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO265825"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>No liability to arise under subsection with respect to disclosure which results from good faith <P>
<A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO265952"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Defendant to be liable to plaintiff in amount equal to sum <P>
<A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO266111"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>$1,000 for each act of unauthorized disclosure of financial record with respect to which such defendant found liable <P>
<A HREF = "SPP90.HTM#AO266313"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Actual damages sustained by plaintiff as result of such unauthorized disclosure <P>
<A HREF = "SPP90.HTM#AO266415"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>In case of willful disclosure or disclosure being result of gross negligence <P>
<A HREF = "SPP90.HTM#AO267111"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Benefit association, insurance company, safe deposit company, money-market mutual fund or similar entity authorized <P>
<A NAME = "AE13080"></A><A NAME = "AE13080"></A><A HREF = "SPP90.HTM#AO267215"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Term financial record having meaning given such term in section 1101 of Right to Financial Privacy Act of 1978 <P>
<A NAME = "AK2674"></A><h3><center>Subtitle G---Enforcement of Support
Orders</center></h4><P><A NAME = "AK2677"></A><h3>SEC. 361. INTERNAL REVENUE SERVICE COLLECTION OF
ARREARAGES.</h3><P><A HREF = "SPP90.HTM#AO26838"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>No additional fee to be assessed for adjustments to amount previously certified pursuant to such section with respect to same obligor <P>
<A NAME = "AK2687"></A><h3>SEC. 362.
AUTHORITY TO COLLECT SUPPORT FROM FEDERAL EMPLOYEES.</h3><P><A NAME = "AK2691"></A><h3> SEC. 459. CONSENT BY THE UNITED
STATES TO INCOME WITHHOLDING, GARNISHMENT, AND SIMILAR PROCEEDINGS FOR
ENFORCEMENT OF CHILD SUPPORT AND ALIMONY OBLIGATIONS.</h3><P><A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO2693212"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Withholding in accordance with State law enacted pursuant to subsections and section 466 and regulations of Secretary under such subsections and other legal process brought by State agency administering program under State plan approved or individual <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO2694136"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Each governmental entity specified in subsection to be subject to same requirements <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO26979"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Designate agent or agents to receive orders and accept service of process in matters relating to child support or alimony <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO26989"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Annually publish in Federal Register designation of agent or agents mailing address and telephone number <P>
<A NAME = "AE13180"></A><A NAME = "AE13180"></A><A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO269923"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Agent designated pursuant to paragraph of subsection receives notice pursuant to State procedures in effect pursuant to subsection or section 466 or effectively served with order, process or interrogatory, respect to individual's child support or alimony payment obligations <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO270318"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Governmental entity specified in subsection receives notice or served with process, provided in section <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO27048"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Support collection under section to be given priority over other process <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO27058"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Allocation of moneys due or payable to individual among claimants under section to be governed by section and regulations prescribed under such section <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO27068"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Such moneys as remain after compliance with paragraphs and available to satisfy other such processes on first-come <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO270671"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Such process to be satisfied out of such moneys as remain after satisfaction of such processes previously served <P>
<A NAME = "AE13240"></A><A NAME = "AE13240"></A><A NAME = "AE13240"></A><A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO270722"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Governmental entity affected by legal process served for enforcement of individual's child support or alimony payment obligations <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO270912"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>United States or government of District of Columbia or disbursing officer to be liable with respect to payment made from moneys due or payable from United States to individual pursuant to legal process regular on face <P>
<A NAME = "AE13260"></A><A NAME = "AE13260"></A><A NAME = "AE13260"></A><A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO27108"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>No Federal employee of which duties include taking actions necessary to comply with requirements of subsection with regard to individual to be subject under law to disciplinary action or civil or criminal liability or penalty <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO2710107"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Disclosure of information made by employee in connection with carrying out of such actions <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO271324"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Vested jointly in President pro tempore of Senate and Speaker of House of Representatives <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO271623"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Moneys paid or payable to individual considered to be based upon remuneration for employment <P>
