<A HREF = "SPP92.HTM#AO27298"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>CERTAIN AMOUNTS EXCLUDED <P>
<A NAME = "AE13400"></A><A HREF = "SPP92.HTM#AO273142"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Including Federal employment taxes and fines and forfeitures ordered by court-martial <P>
