<A NAME = "AE11810"></A><A NAME = "AE11810"></A><A HREF = "SPP81.HTM#AO239442"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Paternity having not to be established paternity action brought but dismissed because statute of limitations of less than 18 years in effect in State <P>
<A HREF = "SPP81.HTM#AO239915"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Procedures which require State agency <P>
