<A HREF = "SPP81.HTM#AO240113"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>To obtain additional testing in case if original test result contested, request and advance payment by contestant <P>
<A NAME = "AE11850"></A><A NAME = "AE11850"></A><A HREF = "SPP81.HTM#AO240411"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>HOSPITAL, BASED PROGRAM <P>
<A HREF = "SPP81.HTM#AO240423"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Such procedures to include hospital-based program for voluntary acknowledgment of paternity focusing on period after birth of child <P>
