combination of impairments, and that such impairment or combination of impairments no longer results in marked and severe functional 
limitations; or</ul></ul></ul>
<p><ul><ul><ul>   (ii) substantial<A NAME = "AO17019"></A> evidence which demonstrates that, as determined on the basis of new or improved diagnostic techniques or 
evaluations, the individual's impairment or combination of impairments, is not as disabling as it was considered to be at the time of the 
most recent prior decision that the individual<A NAME = "AO1701104"></A> was under a disability or continued to be under a disability, and such impairment or 
