<A NAME = "AE10390"></A><A HREF = "SPP72.HTM#AO212419"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>No report to be filed with respect to employee of State or local agency performing intelligence or counterintelligence functions <P>
<A HREF = "SPP72.HTM#AO212482"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Filing such report to endanger safety of employee or compromise investigation or intelligence mission after paragraph <P>
