<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP98.HTM#AS290534">Identification number: </A><DD>Data match system in which each such financial institution required to provide for each calendar quarter name, record address, social security number or other taxpayer identification number and other identifying information for each noncustodial parent who maintains account at such institution and owes past-due support as identified by
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP112.HTM#AS334450">Identification number: </A><DD>Taxpayer identification number means social security number issued to individual by Social Security Administration that relates to clause of section of Social Security Act
