<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP33.HTM#AS99671">Illegitimacy: </A><DD>Research to include studies on effects of different programs and operation of such programs on welfare dependency, illegitimacy, teen pregnancy, employment rates, child well-being and other area Secretary deems appropriate
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP13.HTM#AS41145">Illegitimacy ratio of State: </A><DD>Special emphasis on teenage pregnancies and establish numerical goals for reducing illegitimacy ratio of State for calendar years 1996 through 2005
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP102.HTM#AS30316">Immigration: </A><DD>Congress makes following statements concerning national policy with respect to welfare and immigration
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP102.HTM#AS303512">Immigration: </A><DD>Availability of public benefits not constitute incentive for immigration to United States
