<A HREF = "SPP79.HTM#AO23905"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Soldiers and priests declared dervish heir to throne <P>
<A HREF = "SPP79.HTM#AO23933"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>One day having become Sultan <P>
<A HREF = "SPP79.HTM#AO239717"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Vizir obeyed and envious man <P>
<A HREF = "SPP80.HTM#AO24033"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Leave of envious man and went on way <P>
<A HREF = "SPP80.HTM#AO24285"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Mountain and found in flat plain bounded <P>
<A HREF = "SPP81.HTM#AO24303"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Vessel moored about half mile from shore <P>
<A HREF = "SPP81.HTM#AO24433"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Feet and grasped tight hold of dress <P>
<A HREF = "SPP81.HTM#AO24487"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Ship surrounded by multitude of small <P>
<A HREF = "SPP81.HTM#AO245015"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>One boat contained several <P>
<A HREF = "SPP81.HTM#AO24577"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Sultan being anxious to find similar talent in successor <P>
<A HREF = "SPP82.HTM#AO24755"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Of writing in use among Arabs and each sort contained <P>
<A HREF = "SPP83.HTM#AO25129"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Crowd filled every doorway and every window <P>
<A HREF = "SPP84.HTM#AO252313"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Over Sultan dismissed court <P>
<A HREF = "SPP84.HTM#AO25255"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Into another room and ordered food <P>
<A HREF = "SPP84.HTM#AO25383"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Supper over chessmen brought and Sultan signed <P>
<A HREF = "SPP84.HTM#AO25445"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Sultan enchanted with talents of which given <P>
<A HREF = "SPP85.HTM#AO25505"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Chief of eunuchs bowed and left room ushering in few <P>
<A HREF = "SPP85.HTM#AO25579"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Eunuch being own servant <P>
<A HREF = "SPP85.HTM#AO25625"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Monkey being no monkey <P>
<A HREF = "SPP86.HTM#AO25983"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Fetched knife with Hebrew words engraven on blade <P>
<A HREF = "SPP87.HTM#AO26339"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>In moment serpent having become eagle more <P>
<A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO263919"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>At heels being wolf <P>
<A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO264017"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Cat changed into worm <P>
<A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO26415"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Piercing skin of pomegranate which tumbled from tree <P>
<A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO264215"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Pomegranate swelled till <P>
<A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO26433"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Large as pumpkin and raised to roof of gallery <P>
<A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO26499"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Lay on bank of little canal that flowed <P>
<A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO26517"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Seed rolled into canal and became fish <P>
<A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO26523"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Flung after fish and took shape of pike <P>
<A HREF = "SPP88.HTM#AO26627"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Of eunuchs burned to cinder <P>
<A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO26813"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Pomegranate seed and eaten like rest <P>
<A HREF = "SPP89.HTM#AO26885"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Eunuch consumed by flames and prince <P>
<A HREF = "SPP90.HTM#AO27003"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Days whole nation mourned and ashes of princess <P>
<A HREF = "SPP90.HTM#AO270311"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Sultan recovered from severe illness <P>
<A HREF = "SPP90.HTM#AO27115"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>To Bagdad and request audience of Commander of Faithful <P>
<A HREF = "SPP90.HTM#AO27155"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Other Calender told story <P>
<A NAME = "AK2720"></A><H3>Story of the Third Calendar, Son of a King</H2><P><A HREF = "SPP90.HTM#AO27275"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Name being Agib and I being son of king called Cassib <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO27435"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>To catch sight of land and reported that nothing to be seen <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO27563"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Iron and nails to fall out of ships and cling to mountain <P>
<A HREF = "SPP91.HTM#AO27577"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Ships to sink to bottom <P>
<A HREF = "SPP92.HTM#AO276215"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Summit stands brass dome supported <P>
<A HREF = "SPP92.HTM#AO27789"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>At bottom of steps which led up mountain <P>
<A HREF = "SPP92.HTM#AO278825"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Thou art awake <P>
<A HREF = "SPP93.HTM#AO27893"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Dig up ground underfoot and thou shalt find bow of brass <P>
<A HREF = "SPP93.HTM#AO27949"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Thou wilt perceive figure of metal man seated <P>
<A HREF = "SPP93.HTM#AO279613"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Thou wouldest behold kingdom <P>
<A HREF = "SPP93.HTM#AO27973"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>See that thou takest not name of Allah into mouth <P>
<A HREF = "SPP93.HTM#AO28177"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>In sun and flung on warm ground to rest <P>
<A HREF = "SPP94.HTM#AO28215"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>With fruit trees and watered with streams <P>
<A HREF = "SPP95.HTM#AO28686"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Prophecy struck heart of father with woe <P>
<A HREF = "SPP97.HTM#AO29215"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Old man and slaves pushed off in boat directly ship <P>
<A HREF = "SPP97.HTM#AO29283"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Carrying body of old man who fainted from sorrow <P>
<A HREF = "SPP98.HTM#AO294117"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Prison having grown larger <P>
<A HREF = "SPP99.HTM#AO29695"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>None of sofas to hold more than one person <P>
<A HREF = "SPP99.HTM#AO29857"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Wept and beat breasts <P>
<A HREF = "SPP99.HTM#AO299611"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Actions as none but madmen to be capable <P>
<A HREF = "SPP100.HTM#AO30185"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>On hearing determination ten hosts took sheep <P>
<A HREF = "SPP100.HTM#AO302615"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Roc sees <P>
<A HREF = "SPP100.HTM#AO30283"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Plates of gold studded with jewels <P>
<A HREF = "SPP101.HTM#AO30367"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>In few minutes roc appeared and bore off <P>
<A HREF = "SPP102.HTM#AO30595"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>With scented water and poured over hands and rest <P>
<A HREF = "SPP103.HTM#AO31043"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Planted with roses, jessamine, dafeodils, hyacinths and anemones <P>
<A HREF = "SPP103.HTM#AO31077"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Treasury heaped up with precious stones <P>
<A HREF = "SPP104.HTM#AO31279"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Gold and silver lamps hung from ceiling <P>
<A HREF = "SPP104.HTM#AO31325"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Saddle and bridle of massive gold <P>
<A HREF = "SPP104.HTM#AO31333"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>One side of trough filled with clean barley and sesame <P>
<A NAME = "AK3181"></A><H3>The Seven Voyages of Sindbad the Sailor</H2><P><A HREF = "SPP106.HTM#AO31847"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>In times of Caliph Haroun-al-Raschid lived in Bagdad <P>
<A HREF = "SPP106.HTM#AO31855"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Poor porter named Hindbad <P>
<A HREF = "SPP106.HTM#AO31895"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>With rose water and cool breeze blowing <P>
<A HREF = "SPP106.HTM#AO31907"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Upon ground and sat down to rest in shade of grand house <P>
<A HREF = "SPP106.HTM#AO31925"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Delicious perfume of aloes wood and pastilles came from open <P>
<A HREF = "SPP106.HTM#AO31933"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Windows and mingled with scent of rose water which steamed <P>
<A HREF = "SPP106.HTM#AO31959"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Of instruments cunningly played and melodious warble <P>
<A HREF = "SPP107.HTM#AO32165"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Misfortunes and hard work to get even enough bad barley <P>
<A HREF = "SPP107.HTM#AO32273"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Hindbad being not little surprised at summons and feared <P>
<A HREF = "SPP107.HTM#AO32283"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Unguarded words to have drawn displeasure of Sindbad <P>
<A HREF = "SPP108.HTM#AO32437"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>At right hand and heaped choice morsels upon plate <P>
<A HREF = "SPP108.HTM#AO32567"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>At question Hindbad covered with confusion and hanging down <P>
<A HREF = "SPP108.HTM#AO32669"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>For years suffered every possible kind of toil and danger <P>
<A HREF = "SPP109.HTM#AO32765"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Sindbad relating adventures on account <P>
<A NAME = "AK3285"></A><H3>First Voyage</H2><P><A HREF = "SPP110.HTM#AO33085"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Furled and captain gave permission <P>
<A HREF = "SPP111.HTM#AO33543"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>News from Bagdad and find out means of returning <P>
<A HREF = "SPP111.HTM#AO33557"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>For capital situated upon sea-shore and visited <P>
<A HREF = "SPP112.HTM#AO33643"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Saving fish being full two hundred cubits long <P>
<A HREF = "SPP112.HTM#AO33673"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Other fishes being only cubit long having heads like owls <P>
<A HREF = "SPP112.HTM#AO33707"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Just cast anchor and discharging cargo <P>
<A HREF = "SPP113.HTM#AO33973"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Eyes see Sindbad drown and audacity to tell <P>
<A HREF = "SPP114.HTM#AO34325"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Sindbad paused and commanded musicians to play <P>
<A HREF = "SPP114.HTM#AO34433"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Voyager's house and received with open arms <P>
<A NAME = "AK3454"></A><H3>Second Voyage</H2><P><A HREF = "SPP115.HTM#AO34675"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>In springs of excellent water, appeared to possess not houses <P>
<A HREF = "SPP117.HTM#AO35205"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>By mountains which towered into clouds and steep <P>
<A HREF = "SPP118.HTM#AO35463"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>More pieces rolled over cliffs in different places <P>
<A HREF = "SPP118.HTM#AO35503"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Tales invented to give pleasure to hearers <P>
<A HREF = "SPP118.HTM#AO355611"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Eagles pounced upon meat and carried <P>
<A HREF = "SPP119.HTM#AO35975"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Of Rohat where camphor trees grow <P>
<A HREF = "SPP120.HTM#AO35997"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>From incision made high up in tree into vessel hung <P>
<A HREF = "SPP120.HTM#AO36245"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Other guests departed to homes <P>
<A HREF = "SPP120.HTM#AO36263"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Work and poverty having already begun to seem like bad dream <P>
<A NAME = "AK3633"></A><H3>Third Voyage</H2><P><A HREF = "SPP121.HTM#AO36403"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Merchandise of Bagdad, I conveyed to Balsora and set sail <P>
<A HREF = "SPP121.HTM#AO36535"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Words caused consternation among ship's company <P>
<A HREF = "SPP121.HTM#AO36563"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Two feet high and covered with reddish fur <P>
<A HREF = "SPP122.HTM#AO36869"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Tall as palm tree and black and one eye <P>
<A HREF = "SPP123.HTM#AO36893"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Lip hung down upon chest and ears like elephans's ears <P>
<A HREF = "SPP123.HTM#AO37085"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Fate until hall echoed with despairing cries <P>
<A HREF = "SPP126.HTM#AO38033"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Plunge from cliffs and end life once than pass another <P>
<A HREF = "SPP127.HTM#AO38125"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Ship afforded and captain <P>
<A HREF = "SPP128.HTM#AO38667"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Fish like cow and skin thick <P>
<A NAME = "AK3882"></A><H3>Fourth Voyage</H2><P><A HREF = "SPP129.HTM#AO38897"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Of Persian provinces having first sent off stores of goods <P>
<A HREF = "SPP129.HTM#AO38967"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>For storm driven near island and scrambling up <P>
<A HREF = "SPP130.HTM#AO39125"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Produced large bowls full of rice prepared with cocoanut oil <P>
<A HREF = "SPP131.HTM#AO395311"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Men rode horses without bridle or stirrups <P>
<A HREF = "SPP133.HTM#AO40067"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Place of interment reached corpse lowered <P>
<A HREF = "SPP133.HTM#AO40119"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Stone laid over opening and melancholy <P>
<A HREF = "SPP136.HTM#AO40829"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Glimmer of light which grew clearer every moment <P>
<A HREF = "SPP136.HTM#AO40857"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Little animal having found way into cavern <P>
<A HREF = "SPP136.HTM#AO40915"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Mountains sloped sheer down to sea and no road <P>
<A HREF = "SPP136.HTM#AO40935"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Amassed rich treasure of diamonds, rubies, emeralds and jewels <P>
<A HREF = "SPP136.HTM#AO41073"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Captain occupied with difficulties of navigation <P>
<A HREF = "SPP137.HTM#AO41185"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Sindbad paused and hearers declared that adventures <P>
<A HREF = "SPP137.HTM#AO41197"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Of fourth voyage pleased better than anything <P>
<A NAME = "AK4130"></A><H3>Fifth Voyage</H2><P><A HREF = "SPP138.HTM#AO41635"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Hold and block of stone hurtled through air <P>
<A HREF = "SPP140.HTM#AO42077"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Old man held on tight to neck <P>
<A HREF = "SPP140.HTM#AO42153"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Bunches of grapes which hung from every bush <P>
<A HREF = "SPP141.HTM#AO42405"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Scene of evil deeds and no merchant or sailor who lands <P>
<A HREF = "SPP141.HTM#AO42447"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>After several days reached large and prosperous-looking <P>
<A HREF = "SPP141.HTM#AO42453"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Town where houses built of stone <P>
<A HREF = "SPP141.HTM#AO42563"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Object of expedition to fill sacks with cocoanuts <P>
<A HREF = "SPP142.HTM#AO42667"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>For monkeys, annoyed and wishing to pay back in own coin <P>
<A HREF = "SPP143.HTM#AO42903"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Sequins to be given to Hindbad and guests withdrew <P>
<A NAME = "AK4297"></A><H3>Sixth Voyage</H2><P><A HREF = "SPP143.HTM#AO43083"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Indian port with captain who meant to make long voyage <P>
<A HREF = "SPP143.HTM#AO43153"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Spot upon whole wide sea and caught by current <P>
<A HREF = "SPP144.HTM#AO43197"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Of sea and vessel dashed to pieces upon rocks <P>

