<A HREF = "SPP198.HTM#AO59415"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Danhasch took form of gnat and bit <P>
<A HREF = "SPP198.HTM#AO59685"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Two genii hastened to obey and Maimoune returned to well <P>
<A HREF = "SPP199.HTM#AO59925"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Of greetings vizir said <P>
<A HREF = "SPP201.HTM#AO60335"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Vizir bowed to ground and hastened to leave room and tower <P>
<A HREF = "SPP201.HTM#AO60493"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Camaralzaman replied with good sense <P>
<A HREF = "SPP203.HTM#AO60923"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Genii having carefully borne Princess of China back <P>
<A HREF = "SPP204.HTM#AO613915"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Queen tried to pacify <P>
<A HREF = "SPP205.HTM#AO61525"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Elderly emir present fired with desire to possess young <P>
<A HREF = "SPP205.HTM#AO61595"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Emir accepted condition and king led to princess <P>
<A HREF = "SPP206.HTM#AO61953"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Marzavan listened with downcast eyes and attention <P>
<A HREF = "SPP206.HTM#AO62043"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Marzavan journeyed from city to city and one island and province <P>
<A HREF = "SPP207.HTM#AO62105"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Of Prince Camaralzaman reported ill and story <P>
<A HREF = "SPP207.HTM#AO62133"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Marzavan rejoiced and set out at once for Prince <P>
<A HREF = "SPP207.HTM#AO622311"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Vizir at once attracted by young man's <P>
<A HREF = "SPP208.HTM#AO62555"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Left alone Marzavan told prince story of Princess <P>
<A HREF = "SPP208.HTM#AO62635"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Of Marzavan's interview and ordered public rejoicings in honour <P>
<A HREF = "SPP209.HTM#AO62853"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Only one night to be spent out for fear of fatigue <P>

<p>




