<p><ul><ul>   (B) wage<A NAME = "AO22368"></A><A NAME = "AS22369"></A><A NAME = "AS223610"></A><A NAME = "AS223611"></A><A NAME = "AS223612"></A><A NAME = "AS223613"></A><A NAME = "AB223614"></A> and unemployment<A NAME = "AB223619"></A> compensation information contained in the records of such agency shall be furnished to the 
