<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP51.HTM#AS153910">Food Stamp Act of 1977: </A><DD>Benefits under food stamp program of Food Stamp Act of 1977 or State program carried out under Food Stamp Act of 1977
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP51.HTM#AS154228">Food Stamp Act of 1977: </A><DD>Amount of benefits required to be provided to household under food stamp program of Food Stamp Act of 1977 or State program carried out under Food Stamp Act of 1977
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP51.HTM#AS154229">Food Stamp Act of 1977: </A><DD>Amount of benefits required to be provided to household under food stamp program of Food Stamp Act of 1977 or State program carried out under Food Stamp Act of 1977
