<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP52.HTM#AS155113">Food Stamp Act of 1977: </A><DD>Section of Food Stamp Act of 1977, referring to food stamp program of Food Stamp Act of 1977 or State program carried out under Food Stamp Act of 1977
