<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Abstract Page</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<A NAME = "AN"></A><A NAME = "AQ"></A>

<A HREF = "HOME.HTM#ANC_HP_TOP"><img src="SMANCR.GIF" align=middle></A> <strong>Return to Anchor Page</strong>
&#160;&#160;


<hr>
<img src="CLOUD.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE><STRONG> ABSTRACT VIEW</STRONG>
<P>
<STRONG>Choosing an entry on this page will take you to that entry in the full-text document.</strong>
<P>
<A HREF = "SPP0.HTM#AO65"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Of one of kings of race said to be best <P>
<A HREF = "SPP0.HTM#AO163"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Tartary from Persian Empire and made brother king <P>
<A HREF = "SPP0.HTM#AO187"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Sultan Schahriar having wife <P>
<A HREF = "SPP1.HTM#AO325"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Poor man fulfilled task with reluctance <P>
