104. SERVICES<A NAME = "AS11457"></A><A NAME = "AS11458"></A><A NAME = "AB11459"></A> PROVIDED BY CHARITABLE, RELIGIOUS, OR PRIVATE<A NAME = "AB114522"></A>
ORGANIZATIONS.</h3> <p><ul>  (a) IN GENERAL--</ul> <p><ul><ul>  (1) STATE
OPTIONS-- A State may--</ul></ul> <p><ul><ul><ul>  (A) administer<A NAME = "AO11499"></A> and provide
services under the programs described in subparagraphs (A) and (B)(i) of
paragraph (2) through contracts with charitable, religious, or private
