<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP129.HTM#AS383918">Census survey: </A><DD>Secretary to provide to each State agency administering child and adult care food program under section data from decennial census survey or other appropriate census survey For which data being available showing
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP129.HTM#AS383919">Census survey: </A><DD>Secretary to provide to each State agency administering child and adult care food program under section data from decennial census survey or other appropriate census survey For which data being available showing
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP79.HTM#AS236011">Certain records: </A><DD>Certain records held by private entities with respect to individuals who owe or owed support
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP94.HTM#AS279726">Certification of authenticity: </A><DD>Date of certification of authenticity or completeness of copy of court order for child support received by Secretary concerned for purposes of section
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP141.HTM#AS420021">Certification period: </A><DD>State agency having not made use of standard utility allowance mandatory under subclause to allow household to switch at end of certification period between standard utility allowance and deduction based on actual utility costs of household
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP58.HTM#AS1734161">Chairman of Committee on: </A><DD>Chairman of Committee on Budget of House of Representatives to submit adjustments made under subparagraph to House of Representatives and such adjustments published in Congressional Record
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP114.HTM#AS340216">Child Care: </A><DD>Title to be cited as Child Care and Development Block Grant Amendments of 1996'
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP114.HTM#AS340374">Child Care: </A><DD>Reference to be considered to be made to section or other provision of Child Care and Development Block Grant Act of 1990
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP116.HTM#AS345344">Child Care: </A><DD>Amounts provided to State under section to be transferred to lead agency under Child Care and Development Block Grant Act of 1990 integrated by State into programs established by State under such Act
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP128.HTM#AS380310">Child Nutrition Act of 1966: </A><DD>Family or group day care home located in area served by school enrolling elementary students in which at least 50 percent of total number of children enrolled being certified eligible to receive free or reduced price school meals under Act or Child Nutrition Act of 1966
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP132.HTM#AS392314">Child Nutrition Act of 1966: </A><DD>Section 4 of Child Nutrition Act of 1966 amended by striking subsections
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP133.HTM#AS39556">Child Nutrition Act of 1966: </A><DD>Second sentence of section of Child Nutrition Act of 1966 amended by striking at times to be available and inserting to be available at reasonable time
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP135.HTM#AS402631">Child Nutrition Act of 1966: </A><DD>Section 17 of Child Nutrition Act of 1966 amended by striking subsections
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP136.HTM#AS405619">Child Nutrition Act of 1966: </A><DD>Second sentence of section of Child Nutrition Act of 1966 amended by striking at times to be available and inserting to be available at reasonable time
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP136.HTM#AS407211">Child Nutrition Act of 1966: </A><DD>Section 19 of Child Nutrition Act of 1966 amended by striking subsection
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP157.HTM#AS465716">Child Nutrition Act of 1966: </A><DD>Secretary to issue regulations providing criteria for disqualification under Act of approved retail food store or wholesale food concern disqualified from accepting benefits under special supplemental nutrition program for women, infants and children established under section 17 of Child Nutrition Act of 1966
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP74.HTM#AS218368">Child abuse: </A><DD>State having reasonable evidence of domestic violence or child abuse and disclosure of such information to be harmful to custodial parent or child of such parent
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP113.HTM#AS336715">Child abuse: </A><DD>Secretary to conduct national study based on random samples of children at risk of child abuse or neglect or determined by States to be abused or neglected
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP14.HTM#AS44112">Child care: </A><DD>4/3 of total amount required to be paid to State under former section 403 for 1st 3 quarters of fiscal year 1995 or child care under subsection or former section 402
