<ul><ul> (4) CONTINUANCE IN OFFICE OF ASSISTANT
SECRETARY FOR FAMILY SUPPORT-- The individual<A NAME = "AO160329"></A> who, on the day before the
effective date of this title, is serving as Assistant Secretary for Family
Support within the Department of Health and Human Services shall, until a
successor is appointed to such position--</ul></ul> <p><ul><ul><ul> (A)
continue to serve in such position; and</ul></ul></ul> <p><ul><ul><ul> (B)
