<A NAME = "AK1082"></A><h3> SEC. 419. DEFINITIONS.</h3><P><A HREF = "SPP36.HTM#AO108513"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Term adult means individual being not minor child <P>
<A HREF = "SPP36.HTM#AO108615"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Term minor child means individual <P>
<A HREF = "SPP36.HTM#AO108812"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Not attained 19 years of age and full-time student in secondary school <P>
<A HREF = "SPP36.HTM#AO108915"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Term fiscal year means 12-month period ending on September 30 of calendar year <P>
<A NAME = "AE5810"></A><A NAME = "AE5810"></A><A NAME = "AE5810"></A><A HREF = "SPP36.HTM#AO109134"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Indian tribe and tribal organization having meaning given such terms by section 4 of Indian Self-Determination and Education Assistance Act <P>
<A HREF = "SPP37.HTM#AO110523"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Term State means 50 States of United States <P>
<A NAME = "AK1111"></A><h3> SEC. 1108. ADDITIONAL GRANTS TO PUERTO RICO, THE VIRGIN ISLANDS, GUAM, AND AMERICAN SAMOA; LIMITATION ON TOTAL PAYMENTS.</h3><P><A HREF = "SPP37.HTM#AO111338"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Total amount certified by Secretary of Health and Human Services under titles I, X <P>
<A NAME = "AE5850"></A><A HREF = "SPP37.HTM#AO111513"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Each territory to be entitled to receive from Secretary for each fiscal year grant in amount equal to 75 percent of amount <P>
<A NAME = "AE5860"></A><A HREF = "SPP37.HTM#AO111611"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Total expenditures of territory during fiscal year under territory programs funded under parts A and E of title IV <P>
<A HREF = "SPP37.HTM#AO111912"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Total amount expended by territory during fiscal year 1995 pursuant to parts A and F of title IV <P>
<A HREF = "SPP37.HTM#AO112418"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Term family assistance grant having meaning given such term by section <P>
<A NAME = "AE5890"></A><A HREF = "SPP37.HTM#AO11308"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>TOTAL AMOUNT EXPENDED by TERRITORY <P>
<A HREF = "SPP37.HTM#AO113026"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Term total amount expended by territory <P>
<A HREF = "SPP38.HTM#AO113111"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Not include expenditures during fiscal year from amounts made available by Federal Government <P>
<A NAME = "AE5920"></A><A HREF = "SPP38.HTM#AO113412"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Expenditures during fiscal year 1995 For which territory to have received reimbursement from Federal Government <P>
<A HREF = "SPP38.HTM#AO113524"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Territory to which amount paid under subsection of section to use amount in accordance with section <P>
<A HREF = "SPP38.HTM#AO113616"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Ceiling amount with respect to territory to be reduced for fiscal year by amount equal to amount <P>
<A HREF = "SPP38.HTM#AO113710"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Total amount expended by territory under programs of territory operated pursuant to provisions of law specified in subsection for fiscal year 1995 <P>
<A HREF = "SPP38.HTM#AO113810"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Total amount expended by territory under programs of territory funded under provisions of law specified in subsection for fiscal year that precedes fiscal year referred in matter preceding paragraph <P>
<A NAME = "AK1145"></A><h3>SEC.
104. SERVICES PROVIDED BY CHARITABLE, RELIGIOUS, OR PRIVATE
ORGANIZATIONS.</h3><P><A HREF = "SPP38.HTM#AO11499"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Administer and provide services under programs described in subparagraphs and paragraph through contracts with charitable, religious or private organizations <P>
<A HREF = "SPP38.HTM#AO11509"><img src="ABSTRACT.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Provide beneficiaries of assistance under programs described in subparagraphs and paragraph with certificates, vouchers or other forms of disbursement being redeemable with such organizations <P>

