which was given to us at once with the best grace in the world.
<P>

<P>

This, madam, is my story.
<P>

<P>

&quot;I am satisfied,&quot; replied<A NAME = "AS195312"></A> Zobeida<A NAME = "BB195315"></A><A HREF = "SPP260.HTM#BB780028"><img src="LINK.GIF"></A>; &quot;you can go when you like.
