individual for any period of time under the State program funded under this part.</ul></ul></ul>
<p><ul><ul><ul>   (F) RULE OF INTERPRETATION-- This part shall not be interpreted<A NAME = "AO77326"></A> to prohibit any State from expending State funds not 
originating with the Federal Government on benefits for children or families that have become ineligible for assistance under the State 
program funded under this part by reason of subparagraph (A).</ul></ul></ul>
<p><ul><ul>   (8) DENIAL<A NAME = "AO7748"></A><A NAME = "AS7749"></A><A NAME = "AS77410"></A><A NAME = "AS77411"></A><A NAME = "AS77412"></A><A NAME = "AS77413"></A><A NAME = "AB77414"></A> OF ASSISTANCE FOR 10 YEARS TO A <A NAME = "AB77430"></A>PERSON FOUND TO HAVE FRAUDULENTLY<A NAME = "AB77440"></A> MISREPRESENTED RESIDENCE IN ORDER TO OBTAIN<A NAME = "AB77453"></A> 
ASSISTANCE IN 2 OR MORE<A NAME = "AB77465"></A> STATES-- A State to which a grant is made under section 403 shall not use any part of the grant<A NAME = "AO774107"></A><A NAME = "AS774108"></A> to provide cash 
